Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau datang juga rupanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang mengalahkan Elder Wood, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria terkuat dan paling berbahaya
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang pernah kutemui.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.11,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi incaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.11,0:02:26.05,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Apa ini ulah Lucas?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atas perintah siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ada urusan lagi\Ndengan pecundang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tak berbohong.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.21,0:02:38.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatannya tak sebanding dengan Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada hasil lumayan dari Keluarga Wykes,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi ada masalah yang lebih mendesak.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebab seorang petualang
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,berhasil mengalahkan Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.75,0:02:57.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.85,0:03:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah, Reynolds. Ibu, Alice.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lahir 12 tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membangkitkan Mana Core\Npada usia dua tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu, pindah ke Kota Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.78,0:03:15.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diserang bandit dalam perjalanan,\Nlalu menghilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga tahun kemudian,\Nbersatu lagi dengan keluarga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menjadi petualang di usia 10 tahun,\Nmendaftar dengan nama Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.55,0:03:28.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraktivitas sebagai petualang\Nbersama Jasmine Flamesworth.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.11,0:03:33.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kedua orang tuamu\Nmantan anggota Twin Horn, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari situ dia tahu, rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau selidiki aku sampai sedetail itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau penggemarku?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak berniat bertarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma ingin tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam catatan Guild,\Nkau tertera sebagai Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.78,0:03:54.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain, kau tercatat\Nmengalahkan Elder Wood sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kau melakukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald dan yang lainlah pelakunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria itu tak punya kekuatan\Nuntuk melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bisa bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu betul kekuatannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebab akulah yang mengarahkannya\Nke tempat itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,memaafkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir suara?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan cuma itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu aktivasi sihirnya singkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menguasai banyak atribut.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir yang tak kukenal, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan momen ini, pasti...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemampuan pedang dan pengendalian mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.95,0:05:39.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keduanya tergolong kelas atas.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bukan cuma itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu karena sudah\Nmelihat banyak Mana Beast.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kekuatan asing di dalam
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana Core milikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang sudah mengalahkan Elder Wood,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katamu sudah melihat banyak Mana Beast, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.81,0:06:06.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemunculan ganjil Beast\Ndi padang gembala itu juga ulahmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.01,0:06:10.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tempat yang pas\Nuntuk menguji hasil penelitian.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, jawab aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kau mengalahkan Elder Wood?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyembunyikan kekuatanmu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.53,0:06:36.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sebodoh itu memamerkan kekuatan\Npada orang tak dikenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawab aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya kau tak berteriak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang memanggilku ke tempat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga tak mau diketahui\Norang lain, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawab.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak salah lagi,\Nkaulah yang mengalahkan Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.33,0:07:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasa ingin tahu membutakanku,\Naku malah mencari masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tujuanku mengendalikan Mana Beast,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,demi menyempurnakan sihir itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa kendalikan penuh\Nyang Kelas A ke bawah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.60,0:07:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tak bisa yang Kelas S.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, bukan kau\Nyang mengendalikan Elder Wood?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.95,0:07:53.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tekad mereka jadi penghalang\Nuntuk mengendalikan Kelas S.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.98,0:07:59.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, kuhapus Tekad mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.15,0:08:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mengendalikan Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.21,0:08:12.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurampas Tekadnya,\Nlalu kuberi arahan atas perbuatannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.21,0:08:16.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yaitu membunuh semua makhluk\Nyang masuk ke gua itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.65,0:08:23.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai ganti Tekadnya,\Nkutambah mananya dengan ramuan kegilaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru kali ini kupakai pada manusia,\Ntapi mau bagaimana lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.31,0:08:33.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena identitasku tak boleh ketahuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.01,0:08:39.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahaya, aku harus menghentikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur, di mana Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah, di mana Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Dia tak ada?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.45,0:10:36.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di belakang sana ada orang-orang\Nyang berharga bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak akan kubiarkan lewat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan fisiknya\Nsetara Mana Beast Kelas S.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah, dia bisa pakai sihir
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan kekuatan tak wajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.15,0:12:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang dan sihir tak mempan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuatu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus memikirkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.16,0:12:14.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kehilangan itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,direnggut begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,rasanya seperti ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.98,0:13:09.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika akhir ini
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.60,0:13:13.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,disebabkan sesuatu\Ndari kehidupan masa laluku,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu sudah amat jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.61,0:13:28.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nenek?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.61,0:13:36.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau makin kuat, apa yang akan\Nkau perbuat dengan kekuatan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.81,0:13:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin melindungi orang-orang\Nyang berharga bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Absolute Zero!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah merenggut banyak nyawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menghancurkan banyak negara.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walaupun begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh kalah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tamatlah riwayatmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.51,0:16:33.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan penuhi hatimu\Ndengan kebencian dan amarah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah berapa kali aku melanggarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Janjiku denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Sylvia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh terus berada di sini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terluka parah, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau? Ini bukan saatnya begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kota sedang geger besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya akan sulit menutupi semua itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak peduli soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.63,0:17:18.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang bersemayam di dalamnya\Nbukan sekadar Beast biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.38,0:17:23.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan melampaui Beast Kelas S,\Nseperti dalam legenda dan dongeng.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mungkin?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin itu naga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sehari setelah serangan itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.01,0:17:54.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku nyaris tak lolos\Ndari ribuan pertanyaan Alice dan Eleanor.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia membantuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.55,0:18:03.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala Sekolah Cynthia membantu\Nmenangkap Mana Beast yang mengamuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari luar, terlihat begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Reynolds tak berkata apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau dia menyadari sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku bisa mendapat semacam petunjuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ke sana lagi karena berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tak kudapat apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.78,0:18:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingatan itu memang tak bisa dilupakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.95,0:18:34.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi terkubur\Ndi antara peristiwa penting lainnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlepas dari pertarungan,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,waktu yang kulalui\Nbersama orang-orang berharga
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.73,0:18:52.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah sesuatu yang tak tergantikan\Noleh apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir suara?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepada kalian semua,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.15,0:19:26.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,calon pemimpin, cendekiawan,\Ndan tokoh di Dicathen,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,selamat datang di sekolah kecil kami ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.91,0:19:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya Cynthia Goodsky,\NKepala Sekolah akademi ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahun ini akan jadi tahun yang istimewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebanyak ini Elf dan Dwarf yang masuk,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,baru pertama kali terjadi\Nsejak sekolah ini berdiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang paling tepat\Nuntuk menyambut kalian
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.38,0:19:50.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah perwakilan para murid.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.37,0:19:55.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beri tepuk tangan\Nuntuk anggota Dewan Siswa sekolah kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.01,0:21:43.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sylvie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemarilah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang sudah aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah boleh pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak kecil bisa dengan mudah\Nditelan pohon hantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu dari mana asalmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tersesat saat mengejar serangga.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.52,0:22:24.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh ya, siapa namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.61,0:22:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia Eralith.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.31,0:22:35.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aneh sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.61,0:22:37.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengingatnya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.95,0:22:39.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.85,0:22:42.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama tak jumpa, Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama tak jumpa,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.91,0:22:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tess.
